WEBVTT

00:00.868 --> 00:03.604
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:30.931 --> 00:32.900
MAN:
Suspect just turned,

00:32.900 --> 00:35.035
westbound on Selma
from Cahuenga.

00:35.035 --> 00:38.872
[ SIREN WAILING ]
MAN #2: Air-3, what's the speed
of the suspect's vehicle,

00:38.872 --> 00:40.274
and what are the conditions?

00:40.274 --> 00:43.010
NO, NO, NO, DO NOT CALL OFF
THIS [BLEEP] CHASE!

00:43.010 --> 00:44.412
CLEAR!

00:44.412 --> 00:48.349
70, 75. Traffic's moderate,
non-residential.

00:48.349 --> 00:51.485
A43, SHOW US AS
A SECONDARY UNIT IN PURSUIT.

00:51.485 --> 00:53.821
Approaching a no-fly zone.
Got to back off.

00:53.821 --> 00:56.390
Primary unit,
you have it.
WE GOT THIS [BLEEP]

00:56.390 --> 00:57.791
[ TIRES SCREECH ]
CLEAR. WE'RE CLEAR.

00:57.791 --> 01:01.862
A35, SUSPECT HEADING
NORTHBOUND NOW -- SCHRADER.

01:01.862 --> 01:04.898
WE GOT THIS SON OF A BITCH.

01:04.898 --> 01:05.966
[ WAILING CONTINUES ]

01:05.966 --> 01:07.168
CLEAR!

01:08.702 --> 01:10.604
DEWEY!

01:10.604 --> 01:13.241
EVEN WHEN COPS
DO EVERYTHING RIGHT,

01:13.241 --> 01:14.975
THINGS CAN STILL GO SIDEWAYS.

01:14.975 --> 01:18.546
LEARNING TO ACCEPT THIS
IS A BIG PART OF THE JOB.

01:19.613 --> 01:21.149
RUSSELL:
Hold on, hold on.

01:21.149 --> 01:22.716
You of all people,
will you please pull over?

01:22.716 --> 01:24.685
OH, NO, NO, NO. WAIT, WAIT,
WAIT. NO. IT GETS BETTER.

01:24.685 --> 01:28.489
"EXACTLY HOW THE GRISLY PHOTOS
OF THE POP STAR'S HEADLESS BODY

01:28.489 --> 01:30.858
"GOT LEAKED TO TMZ
REMAINS A MYSTERY.

01:30.858 --> 01:33.727
"BUT SECRET SOURCES TELL US
THEY WERE SNAPPED

01:33.727 --> 01:35.929
"WITH DETECTIVE ADAMS'
CELLPHONE.

01:35.929 --> 01:37.498
"DOESN'T TAKE A GENIUS.

01:37.498 --> 01:39.833
Might be time for her to start
scanning the want ads."

01:39.833 --> 01:41.469
WHO READS THIS SHIT ANYWAY?

01:41.469 --> 01:44.372
Are you kidding me?
It's L.A. Who doesn't?

01:44.372 --> 01:45.739
WELL, AT LEAST
THE DEPARTMENT DOESN'T CARE.

01:45.739 --> 01:47.875
HEY, AREN'T YOU ON YOUR WAY
TO A HOMICIDE?

01:47.875 --> 01:50.544
YEAH, AND THE DEAD GUY
WILL PROBABLY HAVE ONE
OF THESE IN HIS POCKET.

01:50.544 --> 01:52.413
What happened
to Lydia the optimist?

01:52.413 --> 01:55.716
SHE GOT HER ASS HANDED TO HER
BY LYDIA THE SUSPECT.

01:55.716 --> 01:57.518
You think Fernandez
is gonna fight for me

01:57.518 --> 01:58.952
with I.A. breathing
down her neck?

01:58.952 --> 02:01.189
WELL, LOOK, I MEAN,
YOU ANSWERED THEIR QUESTIONS.

02:01.189 --> 02:03.491
Okay, you showed them
your bank accounts.

02:03.491 --> 02:05.092
THERE'S NO PROOF
THAT YOU GOT PAID.

02:05.092 --> 02:07.361
I MEAN, LOTS OF PEOPLE
HAD ACCESS TO THE MURDER BOOK

02:07.361 --> 02:08.796
WHERE YOU PUT THE PHOTOS.

02:08.796 --> 02:10.831
SO THERE'S NO PROOF
THAT YOU LEAKED THEM.

02:10.831 --> 02:12.300
I MEAN...

02:12.300 --> 02:14.202
It's gonna be okay.
[ SIGHS ]
YEAH.

02:14.202 --> 02:16.003
MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

02:16.003 --> 02:17.938
PETEY, COME ON,
BREAKFAST!
TOMMY, NO BANGING.

02:17.938 --> 02:19.407
Petey:
I CAN'T FIND MY SHOES.

02:19.407 --> 02:22.142
UH, THAT'S BECAUSE
IT'S IN THE FIREPLACE.

02:22.142 --> 02:24.378
WE -- WE WERE
JUST HORSING AROUND.

02:24.378 --> 02:25.746
GOD, IT DOESN'T STOP.

02:25.746 --> 02:27.548
I GUESS THESE TWO
ARE GONNA FIX THE FENCE

02:27.548 --> 02:28.949
AND MAYBE
THE SPRINKLERS.

02:28.949 --> 02:31.552
EVERYBODY
WANTS TO HELP OUT.

02:31.552 --> 02:34.822
[ MEN SPEAKING SPANISH ON TV ]

02:43.130 --> 02:45.233
YOU PROMISED ME
TO MY FACE

02:45.233 --> 02:46.534
AT THE LAST
COMMUNITY MEETING

02:46.534 --> 02:48.202
THAT YOU'D GET THAT THING
HAULED AWAY.

02:48.202 --> 02:49.403
[ SPEAKS SPANISH ]

02:49.403 --> 02:51.472
BUT STILL ONE MONTH LATER,

02:51.472 --> 02:53.874
MY KIDS GOT TO WATCH GUYS
PISSING IN THE ALLEY

02:53.874 --> 02:56.009
AND STRAWBERRIES
TURNING TRICKS.

02:56.009 --> 02:58.312
THE CITY TOLD ME THAT THEY WERE
GONNA TAKE CARE OF THAT.

02:58.312 --> 03:03.150
MORE COPS.
JUST LIKE CLOCKWORK.

03:03.150 --> 03:04.752
YOU GONNA
PASS THE BUCK, TOO?

03:04.752 --> 03:06.754
'CAUSE HE
JUST KEEPS ON TELLING ME,

03:06.754 --> 03:08.856
AND SOMEHOW,
THAT THING'S STILL HERE.

03:08.856 --> 03:11.592
I LIKE THIS LADY, BUT SHE'S
STARTING TO GET ON MY NERVES.

03:11.592 --> 03:13.627
STILL, SUCKS THAT HER KIDS
GOT TO SEE THIS.

03:13.627 --> 03:16.330
YOU KNOW WHAT SUCKS IS WE
GET THE GUN, THE BIG STICK,

03:16.330 --> 03:18.031
AND THEY THINK
WE HAVE ALL THE POWER.

03:18.031 --> 03:22.002
THEN WHEN THEY REALIZE WE DON'T,
THEY GET ALL MOUTHY WITH US.

03:22.002 --> 03:24.171
THAT'S WHAT SUCKS.

03:24.171 --> 03:25.473
HEY, HOW YOU DOING?
GOOD. WHAT'S UP?

03:25.473 --> 03:26.840
GOOD. YEAH.
HANG ON A SECOND.

03:26.840 --> 03:28.108
YOU GUYS RAIDED THIS HOUSE
AND THIS TRAILER

03:28.108 --> 03:29.510
ABOUT TWO MONTHS AGO,
RIGHT?

03:29.510 --> 03:31.078
YEAH. 40K OF ROCK,
ALL IN A DAY'S WORK.

03:31.078 --> 03:32.713
EXCUSE ME.

03:32.713 --> 03:34.282
THIS -- THIS HOUSE,
IT'S SLATED FOR DEMO, ISN'T IT?

03:34.282 --> 03:35.883
YEAH, THAT'S THE WORD.

03:35.883 --> 03:37.518
THAT'S THE WORD.
SO WHAT'S UP WITH THE TRAILER?

03:37.518 --> 03:38.986
YOU GUYS HAVING TROUBLE
GETTING THAT CLEARED?

03:38.986 --> 03:40.288
IT'S NOT OUR CALL, MAN.

03:40.288 --> 03:41.522
WE'RE STILL WAITING
ON PAPERWORK.

03:41.522 --> 03:43.023
TILL THEN,
IT'S PRIVATE PROPERTY.

03:43.023 --> 03:44.525
OH, PRIVATE PROPERTY.

03:44.525 --> 03:46.427
SO YOU GUYS GOT YOURSELVES
A WARRANT, THEN, RIGHT?

03:46.427 --> 03:48.496
YOU MIND
IF I TAKE A LOOK AT THAT?

03:48.496 --> 03:50.097
SEE, HERE'S MY PROBLEM,
FELLAS.

03:50.097 --> 03:52.633
YOU GOT YOURSELF A LITTLE
FELONY BUS STOP HERE.

03:52.633 --> 03:55.403
ANYTIME YOU NEED A FELONY BUST,
YOU JUST DRIVE ON BY.

03:55.403 --> 04:00.207
WELL, LIKE YOU, WE DON'T
MAKE THE LAWS, REMEMBER?

04:00.207 --> 04:02.710
EXCUSE US.

04:04.812 --> 04:06.947
WE'RE DONE, HUH?

04:06.947 --> 04:09.249
WHAT THE HELL, SAL?

04:10.551 --> 04:11.952
A DOUBLE MURDER
ON VERMONT,

04:11.952 --> 04:13.887
AND YOU GIVE IT
TO FALOONA AND MILLS?

04:13.887 --> 04:15.956
I'M NEXT IN THE ROTATION.
I TOOK YOU OUT.

04:15.956 --> 04:19.627
WHY? BECAUSE SOME B.S.S. ASSHOLE
DOESN'T WANT ME RIDING ALONE?

04:19.627 --> 04:21.595
SAMMY --
YOU'RE LISTENING
TO THESE PEOPLE?

04:21.595 --> 04:23.331
THE SHRINK I TALKED TO
FOR 10 MINUTES,

04:23.331 --> 04:25.032
HE DOESN'T KNOW SHIT
ABOUT BEING A COP.

04:25.032 --> 04:26.434
SIT DOWN.

04:26.434 --> 04:28.201
HE PROBABLY HASN'T BEEN SOUTH
OF THE 10.

04:28.201 --> 04:30.538
LOOK, SAMMY.

04:30.538 --> 04:32.540
SOME GIT COPS
CAME IN LAST NIGHT

04:32.540 --> 04:35.108
AND BROUGHT IN A SUSPECT
IN NATE'S MURDER.

04:35.108 --> 04:36.844
SHIT.

04:42.015 --> 04:44.885
S-SO, DID THEY RAID
THE GUY'S PLACE?

04:44.885 --> 04:46.954
THEY DID
BUT CAME UP WITH NOTHING.

04:46.954 --> 04:49.323
NOTHING? NO BLOOD?
NOTHING ON HIS CLOTHES?

04:49.323 --> 04:52.726
LAB'S STILL CHECKING, ALL RIGHT,
BUT IT DOESN'T LOOK GOOD.

04:52.726 --> 04:54.695
LOOK, ALL THEY REALLY GOT
IS A SNITCH

04:54.695 --> 04:57.331
WHO'LL SWEAR THE GUY DID IT,
AND HE'S A BASE-HEAD.

04:57.331 --> 04:59.132
NOT MUCH OF A WITNESS,
YOU KNOW?

04:59.132 --> 05:01.569
WELL, WHEN CAN I
I.D. HIM?

05:01.569 --> 05:03.671
THEY'RE PUTTING TOGETHER
A SIX-PACK,

05:03.671 --> 05:05.739
SO IT'S JUST GONNA TAKE
AN EXTRA BEAT.

05:06.907 --> 05:11.412
SAMMY, WE GOT TO MAKE THIS THING
SQUEAKY CLEAN.

05:11.412 --> 05:14.314
YOU UNDERSTAND?

05:14.314 --> 05:15.783
HEY, THE VARSITY TEAM.

05:15.783 --> 05:17.050
HEY.
HEY.

05:17.050 --> 05:20.521
ALL RIGHT, SO FAR
WE GOT 10 SHELL CASINGS --

05:20.521 --> 05:22.990
.22s AND .38s.

05:22.990 --> 05:24.758
Josie:
AND THIS GUY WAS THE TARGET?

05:24.758 --> 05:26.159
NO,
DOESN'T LOOK TO BE.

05:26.159 --> 05:27.595
I GOT A WITNESS OVER THERE

05:27.595 --> 05:29.963
WHO SAYS THAT THESE TWO ASSHOLES
WENT AFTER EACH OTHER.

05:29.963 --> 05:31.665
BANG, BANG, BANG.
THEY GET AWAY.

05:31.665 --> 05:33.867
AND THIS POOR GUY GETS CAUGHT
IN THE CROSSFIRE.

05:33.867 --> 05:36.670
WEDDING BAND, NO TATS.
I HATE THESE.

05:36.670 --> 05:38.906
YOU GET A STATEMENT
FROM HIM?

05:38.906 --> 05:40.874
YEAH, STARTED TO,
BUT THEN YOU GUYS CAME.

05:40.874 --> 05:43.477
HIS NAME'S HENRY WATTS.
YOU WANT TO TALK?

05:43.477 --> 05:45.178
YEAH.
YOU TAKE THE BODY?

05:45.178 --> 05:46.580
YEAH, SURE.

05:46.580 --> 05:49.082
HEY, MR. WATTS,
HOW YOU DOING?

05:49.082 --> 05:50.484
I'M DETECTIVE ADAMS.

05:50.484 --> 05:51.819
HI.
GOOD TO MEET YOU.

05:51.819 --> 05:53.253
YOU SURE
YOU'RE OKAY?

05:53.253 --> 05:54.522
YEAH, I'M FINE.

05:54.522 --> 05:56.356
IT'S JUST
WHEN THE SHOOTING STARTED,

05:56.356 --> 05:57.625
I DOVE BETWEEN TWO CARS.

05:57.625 --> 05:59.627
GUESS I JUST...
BANGED MY HEAD.

05:59.627 --> 06:01.328
YOU SHOULD LET THE PARAMEDICS
CHECK YOU OUT.

06:01.328 --> 06:02.630
YOU COULD HAVE
A CONCUSSION.

06:02.630 --> 06:04.632
I'D BE SURPRISED
IF THAT WERE TRUE.

06:04.632 --> 06:08.235
I'M TOLD
I'M VERY HARDHEADED.

06:08.235 --> 06:09.703
SO,
WHAT EXACTLY HAPPENED?

06:09.703 --> 06:12.205
UH, WELL, I CAME OUT OF THERE
WITH SOME GROCERIES,

06:12.205 --> 06:13.607
SAW TWO GUYS ARGUING.

06:13.607 --> 06:15.543
NEXT THING I KNOW,
THEY'RE PULLING OUT GUNS.

06:15.543 --> 06:17.077
I MEAN, IT WAS NUTS.

06:17.077 --> 06:19.212
THEY STARTED SHOOTING AT EACH
OTHER FROM LIKE 10 FEET APART.

06:19.212 --> 06:22.416
THAT POOR GUY THERE WAS JUST
TRYING TO GET OUT OF THE WAY.

06:22.416 --> 06:24.618
YOU THINK
YOU COULD I.D. THE GUYS?

06:24.618 --> 06:26.086
I CERTAINLY COULD TRY.

06:26.086 --> 06:30.424
UH, HEY, GUYS, CAN YOU
COME OVER HERE FOR A SEC?

06:30.424 --> 06:31.825
UM, LET THEM
CHECK YOU OUT, OKAY?

06:31.825 --> 06:34.061
YEAH. OKAY, OKAY.
MAYBE THEY SHOULD.

06:34.061 --> 06:35.663
Munoz: HEY, ADAMS.

06:38.666 --> 06:40.267
WE THINK YOU'RE A LOT HOTTER
IN PERSON,

06:40.267 --> 06:41.635
IF YOU DON'T
MIND US SAYING.

06:41.635 --> 06:43.103
MUNOZ, COME ON,
ISN'T THERE SOMETHING ELSE

06:43.103 --> 06:45.005
YOU COULD BE DOING,
LIKE TRAFFIC CONTROL MAYBE?

06:45.005 --> 06:47.508
OH! LYDIA, WE DON'T
THINK YOU DID IT.
LET'S GO.

06:48.809 --> 06:51.411
HEY. WHAT'S GOING ON?

06:51.411 --> 06:53.013
THIS MAN DOESN'T
HAVE A CONCUSSION.

06:53.013 --> 06:59.653
HE HAS A BULLET
IN HIS HEAD.

06:59.653 --> 07:01.555
YOU TOLD ME THAT THE HOUSE
AND THE TRAILER

07:01.555 --> 07:03.356
WERE BOTH
GONNA BE CLEARED --

07:03.356 --> 07:05.893
MA'AM --

07:05.893 --> 07:07.194
OKAY.

07:07.194 --> 07:09.229
WELL, YOU GOT MY NUMBER.

07:09.229 --> 07:10.698
THANKS.

07:10.698 --> 07:14.067
AND WE WONDER
WHY PEOPLE GO POSTAL.

07:14.067 --> 07:15.669
GREAT.
NOW THIS.

07:15.669 --> 07:17.938
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

07:20.641 --> 07:22.543
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY!

07:22.543 --> 07:25.879
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

07:30.083 --> 07:32.720
ALL RIGHT!
STOP IT RIGHT NOW!
STOP IT!

07:32.720 --> 07:34.187
WHAT ARE YOU DOING IN FRONT
OF THESE KIDS, HUH?

07:34.187 --> 07:36.123
WHAT ARE WE TEACHING THEM?
SHARE AND SHARE ALIKE.

07:36.123 --> 07:37.558
THEY DON'T GOT THAT
IN ARMENIA?

07:37.558 --> 07:38.892
I'M TURKISH.
I'M FROM JORDAN.

07:38.892 --> 07:41.061
THAT'S FINE!
YOU WORK IT OUT.

07:41.061 --> 07:43.330
JUST SWITCH OFF DAYS
OR SOMETHING.

07:43.330 --> 07:45.165
YOU GUYS CAN DO THAT,
RIGHT?

07:45.165 --> 07:47.300
FINE.

07:47.300 --> 07:48.869
I'LL TAKE THE WEEKENDS.

07:48.869 --> 07:50.337
[BLEEP] YOU,
YOU STUPID TERRORIST!

07:50.337 --> 07:51.672
TERRORIST?!
YEAH.

07:51.672 --> 07:53.006
SEE, THIS IS WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

07:53.006 --> 07:54.274
Ben: ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT,
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

07:54.274 --> 07:56.076
HOOK HIM UP.
HOOK HIM UP.

07:56.076 --> 07:59.012
HE'S SELLING GUNS TO KIDS. LOOK.
AND I'M THE TERRORIST?

07:59.012 --> 08:02.315
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I NEED SUGAR.

08:02.315 --> 08:03.617
YOU?

08:03.617 --> 08:06.687
HEY, EVERYBODY!
IT'S YOUR LUCKY DAY!

08:06.687 --> 08:08.756
FREE ICE CREAM,

08:08.756 --> 08:11.491
COURTESY OF THE LOS ANGELES
POLICE DEPARTMENT.

08:11.491 --> 08:13.694
THERE YOU GO, BUDDY.
HAVE A BOMB POP.

08:13.694 --> 08:16.396
AND FURTHERMORE,
THE INVESTIGATING OFFICERS

08:16.396 --> 08:18.098
ARE DELIBERATELY NOT PRESENT,

08:18.098 --> 08:21.569
NOR HAVE THEIR IDENTITIES BEEN
MADE KNOWN TO DETECTIVE BRYANT.

08:21.569 --> 08:24.171
TAKING EVERY PRECAUTION,
THIS SIX-PACK I.D.

08:24.171 --> 08:26.907
WILL BE HANDLED
BY DETECTIVE OLATI JOHNSON

08:26.907 --> 08:28.842
OF THE DOMESTIC VIOLENCE TABLE.

08:28.842 --> 08:30.544
SHE HAS NO KNOWLEDGE
OF THE CASE.

08:30.544 --> 08:32.179
OLATI?

08:32.179 --> 08:35.048
THE PHOTOS YOU'RE ABOUT TO SEE
MAY OR MAY NOT CONTAIN

08:35.048 --> 08:37.918
THE PERSON RESPONSIBLE
FOR NATE MORETTA'S MURDER.

08:37.918 --> 08:41.221
IF YOU UNDERSTAND THIS
AND THE REST OF THE ADMONITIONS,

08:41.221 --> 08:42.556
PLEASE SIGN HERE.

08:53.567 --> 08:56.136
DO YOU SEE ANYONE
YOU RECOGNIZE?

09:06.614 --> 09:09.116
TAKE YOUR TIME, SAMMY.

09:12.119 --> 09:14.087
EXCUSE ME.

09:25.265 --> 09:27.134
YOU ALL RIGHT?

09:27.134 --> 09:30.704
I SAW HIS FACE, SAL.
I JUST...

09:30.704 --> 09:32.305
I JUST NEEDED SOME AIR.

09:32.305 --> 09:33.206
ALL RIGHT.

09:34.675 --> 09:37.110
THAT'S COOL. JUST TAKE
A LITTLE BREATHER, THEN.

09:37.110 --> 09:38.779
WE'LL GO BACK IN,
ALL RIGHT?

09:38.779 --> 09:41.248
TOMORROW.

09:41.248 --> 09:42.816
I NEED A DAY.

09:42.816 --> 09:44.618
SAMMY, YOU'RE NOT SURE,
ARE YOU?

09:44.618 --> 09:47.187
I JUST SAID I SAW HIM.
I JUST...

09:47.187 --> 09:49.790
IT'S JUST HARDER
THAN I EXPECTED.

09:49.790 --> 09:52.826
SAMMY, THIS GUY HAS AN ATTORNEY
BREATHING DOWN MY NECK.

09:52.826 --> 09:55.295
WITHOUT AN I.D.,
WE MIGHT HAVE TO KICK HIM.

09:55.295 --> 09:56.964
CAN'T WE JUST STALL?

09:56.964 --> 09:59.432
WE DO IT ALL THE TIME FOR SHIT
THAT DOESN'T EVEN MATTER.

09:59.432 --> 10:02.469
COME ON, SAL.
WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

10:02.469 --> 10:05.038
[ SIGHS ]

10:05.038 --> 10:07.908
ALL RIGHT.
I'LL DO WHAT I CAN, ALL RIGHT?

10:07.908 --> 10:09.977
I NEED YOU TO FOCUS.

10:09.977 --> 10:13.380
WE NEED THIS, SAMMY,
ALL RIGHT?

10:15.048 --> 10:16.149
YEAH.

10:16.149 --> 10:18.518
John: WE WENT LIGHTS AND SIRENS
FOR THIS?

10:18.518 --> 10:19.987
DUDE, ARE YOU
KIDDING ME, MAN?

10:19.987 --> 10:21.588
I HAD TO GET YOU HERE BEFORE
THE CORONER MOVED THE BODY.

10:21.588 --> 10:22.956
CHECK THIS OUT.

10:22.956 --> 10:25.425
YOU KNOW HOW THEY ALWAYS SAY
TV KILLS BRAIN CELLS?

10:25.425 --> 10:26.694
VOILГ .

10:26.694 --> 10:28.361
YOU GOT TO BE SHITTING ME.

10:28.361 --> 10:30.798
[ LAUGHS ]
Ben:
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

10:30.798 --> 10:32.599
LET ME CLUE YOU IN,
SHERLOCK.

10:32.599 --> 10:35.568
PUSSY GALORE OVER THERE
SAID THAT HE LIKED TO
DO IT WHILE WATCHING PORN.

10:35.568 --> 10:37.037
HE ALSO LIKED THE BOTTOM.

10:37.037 --> 10:39.039
SO HE MOUNTED THE TV
UP THERE,

10:39.039 --> 10:41.241
PULLED IT OUT
OVER THE TOP OF THEM,

10:41.241 --> 10:42.743
BUT I GUESS
HE WASN'T TOO HANDY,

10:42.743 --> 10:44.077
BECAUSE HE USED
THE WRONG SCREWS.

10:44.077 --> 10:45.445
WHERE WAS SHE
WHEN THIS HAPPENED?

10:45.445 --> 10:47.147
SHE SAID IT MISSED HER HEAD
BY AN INCH.

10:47.147 --> 10:51.018
I ALWAYS SAY,
BLOW JOBS CAN SAVE LIVES.

10:51.018 --> 10:52.652
[ LAUGHS ]

10:52.652 --> 10:54.087
Lydia: HEY.

10:54.087 --> 10:55.188
HOW YOU DOING?

10:55.188 --> 10:57.157
FOR A GUY WITH A .22 SLUG
IN HIS HEAD?

10:57.157 --> 11:00.227
I GUESS
THE ANSWER'S...GOOD.

11:00.227 --> 11:02.195
THEY SAID
IF YOU'RE FEELING UP TO IT

11:02.195 --> 11:04.497
THAT WE CAN ASK YOU
A COUPLE QUESTIONS.

11:04.497 --> 11:07.367
THAT'LL DISTRACT ME.
PLEASE, SHOOT.

11:07.367 --> 11:08.568
I MEAN...

11:08.568 --> 11:10.303
[ IMITATES GUNSHOT ]

11:10.303 --> 11:11.471
YOU'RE AN ARTIST?

11:11.471 --> 11:14.074
UH, COMPUTER GRAPHICS MOSTLY.
GOT TO EAT.

11:14.074 --> 11:17.577
BUT EVERY NOW AND THEN,
I GO OLD SCHOOL.

11:17.577 --> 11:20.781
NOTHING LIKE
A PENCIL AND PAD.

11:20.781 --> 11:23.250
THIS WHAT YOU
WANT TO KNOW?

11:23.250 --> 11:25.318
WOW.

11:25.318 --> 11:26.453
THAT'S AMAZING.

11:26.453 --> 11:29.022
SO THE GUYS WERE BLACK?
LIGHT-SKINNED, YEAH.

11:29.022 --> 11:31.859
ONE OF THEM HAD A TATTOO.
I COULDN'T SEE IT CLEARLY.

11:31.859 --> 11:33.761
AND THEY WERE DRESSED
LIKE THIS?

11:33.761 --> 11:35.128
WIFE-BEATERS
AND BLING?

11:35.128 --> 11:37.430
YEAH. ONE OF THEM
WORE AN ANGELS CAP.

11:37.430 --> 11:38.631
THIS IS AMAZING.

11:38.631 --> 11:40.633
DID EITHER OF THEM
HAVE A CAR?

11:40.633 --> 11:42.635
NOT THAT I SAW.

11:42.635 --> 11:44.738
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

11:44.738 --> 11:45.939
HEY. HI.

11:45.939 --> 11:47.808
UM, DOC WANTS
TO SEE US A SEC.

11:47.808 --> 11:49.777
OKAY.

11:49.777 --> 11:51.144
I THINK WE'RE ABOUT TO GET

11:51.144 --> 11:52.913
THE "LEAVE HIM ALONE
AND LET HIM REST" SPEECH.

11:52.913 --> 11:55.482
AH, BEFORE NEUROSURGERY?
PROBABLY SMART.

11:55.482 --> 11:57.785
IS THERE ANYONE
I CAN CALL FOR YOU?

11:57.785 --> 12:00.020
OH, MY FIANCГ©E'S IN ROME
FOR WORK.

12:00.020 --> 12:02.790
I CALLED HER.
SHE'LL BE ON HER WAY BACK SOON.

12:02.790 --> 12:04.792
GOOD.
I'LL BE BACK IN A BIT.

12:08.261 --> 12:09.997
I'D GET WHAT YOU NEED
FROM HIM

12:09.997 --> 12:11.298
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.

12:11.298 --> 12:12.732
YEAH, I WAS KIND OF
TRYING TO DO THAT.

12:12.732 --> 12:14.234
HE DOESN'T HAVE LONG,
OKAY?

12:14.234 --> 12:16.369
I'M JUST GIVING YOU
THE HEADS-UP.

12:16.369 --> 12:17.670
WHAT?

12:17.670 --> 12:19.239
THE BULLET ENTERED THE SKULL

12:19.239 --> 12:21.975
AND SETTLED POSTERIOR
OF THE OPTIC CHIASM.

12:21.975 --> 12:24.711
HE'S GOT INCREASING
INTRACRANIAL PRESSURE.

12:24.711 --> 12:26.179
IN ENGLISH.

12:26.179 --> 12:28.281
THE THING IS SMALL
AND REALLY DEEP IN HIS BRAIN.

12:28.281 --> 12:31.318
ANY OPERATION TO REMOVE IT
WILL MOST LIKELY KILL HIM.

12:31.318 --> 12:33.854
BUT HE'S -- HE'S --
HE'S TALKING.

12:33.854 --> 12:35.055
HE SEEMS FINE.

12:35.055 --> 12:36.689
THAT'S NOT GONNA LAST.

12:36.689 --> 12:38.058
WELL, ARE YOU
GONNA TELL HIM?

12:38.058 --> 12:39.927
NOT YET.
WE'RE WAITING ON KEITH BLACK,

12:39.927 --> 12:42.195
THE TOP GUY AT CEDARS,
TO TAKE A LOOK AT HIS SCANS.

12:42.195 --> 12:44.431
MAYBE HE'LL HAVE A DIFFERENT
TAKE, BUT I DOUBT IT.

12:44.431 --> 12:47.100
[ PAGER BEEPING ]
SORRY. I GOT TO GO.

12:47.100 --> 12:49.536
UM, FERNANDEZ
WANTS US BACK NOW.

12:49.536 --> 12:51.438
OF COURSE SHE DOES.

12:51.438 --> 12:53.673
IT'S NOT JUST YOU, OKAY?

12:53.673 --> 12:56.176
YOU, THOSE R.H.D. GUYS,

12:56.176 --> 12:59.112
AND THE SIX PATROL OFFICERS
THAT WERE FIRST ON THE SCENE

12:59.112 --> 13:01.581
ARE NOW SUSPENDED
FROM DUTY.

13:01.581 --> 13:03.283
YOU'VE BEEN ASSIGNED HOME

13:03.283 --> 13:05.052
PENDING AN INTERNAL
INVESTIGATION.

13:05.052 --> 13:06.386
Josie: ARE WE GETTING PAID?
ARE WE GETTING PAID?

13:06.386 --> 13:08.121
YEAH, WITH ALL BENEFITS.

13:08.121 --> 13:10.457
THAT'S GOOD WITH ME,
'CAUSE I DIDN'T DO NADA.

13:10.457 --> 13:13.293
I'M JUST GONNA GET CAUGHT UP
ON MY INTERNET SHOPPING.

13:13.293 --> 13:15.295
AM I SUPPOSED TO JUST SIT HOME
AND DO NOTHING?

13:15.295 --> 13:17.597
"ASSIGNED HOME" MEANS
THAT DURING WORKING HOURS,

13:17.597 --> 13:18.932
YOU ARE TO STAY AT HOME.

13:18.932 --> 13:20.901
WELL, ARE YOU GONNA PUT
AN ANKLE BRACELET ON ME?

13:20.901 --> 13:22.469
'CAUSE IF NOT,
I'M GONNA DO AS I PLEASE.

13:22.469 --> 13:24.404
YOU HAVE MY CELLPHONE NUMBER.
YOU CAN REACH ME.

13:24.404 --> 13:26.339
OH, NO.
YOU TOOK MY CELLPHONE.

13:26.339 --> 13:28.909
I'M GONNA HAVE TO NOTE THAT
ON THE FILE.

13:28.909 --> 13:30.577
OH, I'M REALLY WORRIED NOW.

13:41.754 --> 13:42.990
WHAT'S UP?

13:42.990 --> 13:45.225
Sal: PULLED A TRAFFIC WARRANT
ON HIM.

13:45.225 --> 13:48.595
IT'S BULLSHIT, BUT IT'LL
HOLD HIM TILL TOMORROW.

13:48.595 --> 13:51.398
HIS ATTORNEY SAW THE VIDEO
OF YOUR SIX-PACK I.D.

13:51.398 --> 13:55.235
NOW HE'S DEMANDING THAT I DO
A LINEUP WITH HIS CLIENT IN IT.

13:55.235 --> 13:56.669
GOOD.

13:56.669 --> 13:59.973
BETTER THAN LOOKING
AT MUG SHOTS, YOU KNOW?

13:59.973 --> 14:02.342
THE ASSHOLE'S STANDING
RIGHT IN FRONT OF ME.

14:02.342 --> 14:04.945
YEAH.

14:04.945 --> 14:07.047
GET A GOOD NIGHT'S SLEEP,
ALL RIGHT?

14:07.047 --> 14:10.150
THE LINEUP'S TOMORROW,
0900.

14:12.719 --> 14:14.254
[ SIGHS ]

14:14.254 --> 14:17.357
SO...THE DOCTOR
READ YOU THE RIOT ACT?

14:17.357 --> 14:19.592
YES,
BUT I CHARMED HER.

14:19.592 --> 14:21.294
OH.

14:21.294 --> 14:25.232
THE NURSES BROUGHT ME SOME ART
SUPPLIES UP FROM THE KIDS' WARD.

14:25.232 --> 14:28.835
FIGURE AS LONG AS I CAN DRAW,
RIGHT, HOW BAD CAN IT BE?

14:28.835 --> 14:30.904
DEFINITELY, YEAH.

14:30.904 --> 14:32.439
EVERYBODY SEEMS
REALLY OPTIMISTIC.

14:32.439 --> 14:34.174
THEY GOT
THIS FAMOUS NEUROSURGEON

14:34.174 --> 14:35.508
COMING IN
TO REVIEW MY CAT SCAN.

14:35.508 --> 14:37.210
THEN THEY'RE GONNA SETTLE
ON WHAT TO DO.

14:37.210 --> 14:39.412
THE SURGERY'S TRICKY,
OBVIOUSLY.

14:39.412 --> 14:41.481
THEY JUST WANT TO DO
THEIR HOMEWORK.

14:43.016 --> 14:45.252
LOOK, MR. WATTS --

14:45.252 --> 14:46.453
HENRY.

14:46.453 --> 14:47.654
HENRY.

14:47.654 --> 14:49.622
ABOUT THE CASE --

14:49.622 --> 14:52.159
OH, YEAH, I REMEMBERED --

14:52.159 --> 14:54.527
THE GUY IN THE HAT YELLED
THE OTHER GUY'S NAME.

14:54.527 --> 14:57.530
LEON, DION,
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

14:57.530 --> 15:00.968
NO, I NEEDED TO TELL YOU
I'M NO LONGER ON THE CASE.

15:00.968 --> 15:03.203
THERE WILL BE
TWO NEW DETECTIVES,

15:03.203 --> 15:05.672
AND THEY'LL BE
COMING AROUND SOON.

15:05.672 --> 15:08.808
OH. I SEE.

15:08.808 --> 15:11.211
YOU'RE THAT
DETECTIVE ADAMS.

15:11.211 --> 15:13.480
LYDIA, I GUESS.

15:13.480 --> 15:17.217
YES.
MY FAME PRECEDES ME.

15:17.217 --> 15:18.651
I SAW IT ON TV.

15:18.651 --> 15:21.121
ON AN ENDLESS LOOP.

15:21.121 --> 15:23.623
SO, DID YOU
LEAK THE PHOTOS?

15:25.858 --> 15:28.328
NO.

15:29.796 --> 15:32.432
I BELIEVE YOU.

15:32.432 --> 15:34.034
THANKS.

15:34.034 --> 15:36.203
I APPRECIATE IT.

15:36.203 --> 15:38.838
SO, I GUESS
YOU'RE GONNA BE GOING,

15:38.838 --> 15:41.008
NOW THAT YOU'RE
OFF THE CASE?

15:41.008 --> 15:42.342
I'M GONNA STAY A BIT

15:42.342 --> 15:44.811
AND BRIEF THE DETECTIVES
WHEN THEY GET HERE.

15:44.811 --> 15:47.114
MIGHT AS WELL.
AVOID THE PAPARAZZI?

15:47.114 --> 15:48.515
HMM.
THAT TOO.

15:48.515 --> 15:49.716
YEAH.

15:49.716 --> 15:53.053
AND LISTEN, UM...

15:53.053 --> 15:57.224
IN CASE I GO INTO SURGERY BEFORE
JESSIE, MY FIANCГ©E, GETS HERE,

15:57.224 --> 15:59.726
COULD YOU, UM...

15:59.726 --> 16:03.430
COULD YOU LET HER KNOW OUR DOGS
ARE WITH THE NEIGHBORS?

16:03.430 --> 16:06.299
OR COULD YOU GET THE DETECTIVES
TO TELL HER?

16:06.299 --> 16:07.534
SURE, SURE, SURE.

16:07.534 --> 16:09.702
I WILL MAKE SURE
SHE GETS THE MESSAGE.

16:09.702 --> 16:13.573
I'M FEELING...
KIND OF TIRED.

16:13.573 --> 16:16.176
GONNA TRY
AND CATCH A NAP.

16:16.176 --> 16:18.745
OKAY. I'LL CHECK IN
IN A BIT.

16:18.745 --> 16:20.080
YEAH.

16:27.387 --> 16:29.456
[ SIGHS ]

16:38.165 --> 16:39.632
I'VE CALLED THREE TIMES TODAY.

16:39.632 --> 16:41.668
I'VE SPOKEN
TO FIVE DIFFERENT CLERKS.

16:41.668 --> 16:43.403
Dewey: SURE AS SHIT,
THE WINDOWS ARE BLACKED OUT.

16:43.403 --> 16:45.205
I KNOW YOU KEEP SAYING THAT,
BUT I NEED TO KNOW WHEN.

16:45.205 --> 16:46.773
BANGING AROUND
ON THE INSIDE.

16:46.773 --> 16:50.110
SO FINALLY I GET THE DOOR
PRIED OPEN, AND -- BWAH! --

16:50.110 --> 16:52.545
THIS FRICKIN' VULTURE
COMES FLYING OUT

16:52.545 --> 16:54.781
WITH AN EAR
HANGING IN ITS BEAK.

16:54.781 --> 16:56.283
I LOOK INSIDE,

16:56.283 --> 16:58.318
AND THE GUY JUST BLEW HIS HEAD
OFF WITH A 12 GAUGE.

16:58.318 --> 16:59.952
HOW'D THE BIRD GET
IN THERE?

16:59.952 --> 17:02.189
IT GOT IN THROUGH THE HOLE IN
THE ROOF THAT THE GUN MADE, MAN.

17:02.189 --> 17:03.756
IT SCARED THE SHIT
OUT OF ME.
SHIT.

17:03.756 --> 17:05.692
Chickie: SHIT,
BEATS THE HELL OUT OF MINE.

17:05.692 --> 17:08.595
JUST SOME POOR OLD GUY, ASS UP
IN THE AIR, NEXT TO THE TOILET.

17:08.595 --> 17:10.463
BLAH, BLAH, BLAH.
THAT'S A DIME A DOZEN, MAN.

17:10.463 --> 17:11.998
THE EXTRA PRESSURE
CAUSED A HEART ATTACK.

17:11.998 --> 17:13.300
I HEARD IT A MILLION TIMES.

17:13.300 --> 17:14.767
SPEAKING OF SHOTGUNS,
YOU HEARD THIS ONE?

17:14.767 --> 17:18.338
SO, KOREATOWN, ONE OF THOSE
ROOMS YOU RENT BY THE HOUR.

17:18.338 --> 17:20.273
HOW MUCH YOU PAY
FOR THAT?
HEY, RELAX.

17:20.273 --> 17:22.209
WE FIND THIS DEAD GUY,
RIGHT?

17:22.209 --> 17:25.245
HE'S COMPLETELY NAKED,
CHEST BLOWN OUT, LYING ON A BED,

17:25.245 --> 17:28.148
SHARDS OF MIRROR
STICKING OUT OF HIS STOMACH,

17:28.148 --> 17:29.382
HIS NECK, HIS FACE.

17:29.382 --> 17:30.950
I GOT THIS.
I GOT THIS.

17:30.950 --> 17:33.320
HE'S LAYING ON THE BED
NEXT TO HIS SHOTTY, RIGHT?

17:33.320 --> 17:35.355
HE KILLED HIMSELF WITH HIS LEGS
UP IN THE AIR.

17:35.355 --> 17:37.056
HE'S GOT A PENCIL
THROUGH HIS TOES

17:37.056 --> 17:38.525
CROSSED THROUGH
THE TRIGGER GUARD.

17:38.525 --> 17:40.059
HE PULLS THE TRIGGER
WITH HIS FEET.

17:40.059 --> 17:42.395
THE RECOIL OF THE GUN
KICKS IT UP INTO THE CEILING,

17:42.395 --> 17:43.796
SMASHING THE MIRROR.
AM I CLOSE?

17:43.796 --> 17:46.032
HUH? [ LAUGHS ]
I HEARD THAT ONE, MAN.

17:46.032 --> 17:47.900
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO TRY
A LITTLE BIT HARDER,
HELLO?

17:47.900 --> 17:50.203
BUT I'LL STILL BUY
YOUR DIRTY ASS LUNCH.
WHAT?

17:50.203 --> 17:52.339
SHIT.
SHE JUST HUNG UP ON ME.

17:52.339 --> 17:54.507
WHY DO YOU
EVEN CARE, MAN?

17:54.507 --> 17:57.644
I FIND IT NOVEL, DEWEY, EVERY
ONCE IN A WHILE TO GIVE A SHIT.

17:59.346 --> 18:02.182
YOU KNOW, WHEN YOU
CALLED ME AND SAID YOU
WERE AT THE HOSPITAL,

18:02.182 --> 18:04.517
I THOUGHT YOU'D
GONE 51/50 ON ME.

18:04.517 --> 18:07.086
TRUST ME,
I AM THIS CLOSE.

18:07.086 --> 18:08.488
NOZICK AND CHAVEZ?

18:08.488 --> 18:09.789
LEFT THEM THREE VOICEMAILS,

18:09.789 --> 18:11.424
AND NEITHER ONE OF THEM
WILL CALL ME BACK.

18:11.424 --> 18:13.092
YEAH, THEY'RE WORKING A STABBING
IN LYNWOOD,

18:13.092 --> 18:14.527
PROBABLY GOT
THEIR HANDS FULL.

18:14.527 --> 18:18.265
YEAH, BUT THIS IS PRIORITY.
THE WITNESS MAY NOT LAST.

18:18.265 --> 18:19.632
IT'S NOT YOUR CASE NOW.

18:19.632 --> 18:21.968
WHY ARE YOU MAKING IT HARDER
FOR YOURSELF?

18:21.968 --> 18:23.470
'CAUSE IT'S NOT
JUST ABOUT ME,

18:23.470 --> 18:25.272
AND I DON'T WANT TO SEE THEM
SCREW THIS UP.

18:26.773 --> 18:29.842
FERNANDEZ TOLD THE CAP THAT
YOU WEREN'T GONNA GO HOME.

18:29.842 --> 18:32.779
AND I THOUGHT HER HEAD
WAS GONNA EXPLODE, YOU KNOW?

18:32.779 --> 18:35.548
SO SHE SENT YOU HERE
TO CONVINCE ME?

18:35.548 --> 18:37.784
WELL, HER LANGUAGE
WAS A BIT STRONGER.

18:37.784 --> 18:42.589
YEAH, WELL, SNAP A PICTURE
AND LEAK HER A PHOTO OF THIS.

18:44.056 --> 18:45.658
THOUGHT YOU MIGHT
FEEL THAT WAY.

18:45.658 --> 18:49.496
I CANNOT BELIEVE
THIS IS HAPPENING, RUSS.

18:49.496 --> 18:51.698
ALL MY HARD WORK, MY REP.

18:51.698 --> 18:54.467
IT'S ALL
GOING TO CRAP NOW.

18:54.467 --> 18:56.403
LEAK CASES
ARE HARD TO PROVE.

18:56.403 --> 18:58.571
ONCE THE DOG-AND-PONY SHOW'S
OVER,

18:58.571 --> 19:00.307
EVERYTHING WILL SETTLE DOWN.

19:00.307 --> 19:02.342
SO YOU JUST GOT TO
WAIT IT OUT.

19:02.342 --> 19:05.512
IF YOU'RE WRONG, WILL YOU
AT LEAST BE MY LEAD REP?

19:05.512 --> 19:07.580
GO THROUGH ALL OF THIS
WITH ME?

19:07.580 --> 19:11.184
DON'T THEY ASSIGN GUYS
TO DO THAT FROM THE LEAGUE?

19:11.184 --> 19:13.786
YEAH, BUT I DON'T TRUST
ANYBODY ELSE.

19:13.786 --> 19:15.688
NO, I-I DON'T HAVE
ANY EXPERIENCE.

19:15.688 --> 19:17.657
YEAH,
BUT YOU'VE GOT MY BACK.

19:17.657 --> 19:19.959
OF COURSE.

19:19.959 --> 19:23.596
[ CHUCKLES ]
OKAY.

19:28.701 --> 19:30.403
IT'S LATE.

19:30.403 --> 19:33.573
YEAH,
JUST ABOUT DONE HERE.

19:33.573 --> 19:35.342
YOU BEEN
COMING AROUND A LOT.

19:35.342 --> 19:36.876
YOU KNOW,
DOING WHAT I CAN.

19:36.876 --> 19:39.178
JUST TRYING TO HELP HER OUT,
YOU KNOW?

19:39.178 --> 19:43.015
THAT ALL YOU WANT TO DO,
HELP HER?

19:43.015 --> 19:45.017
WHAT'D YOU SAY?

19:45.017 --> 19:47.720
YOU HEARD WHAT I SAID.

19:47.720 --> 19:50.423
YOU ACCUSE ME OF TRYING
TO MOVE IN ON THE WIDOW?

19:50.423 --> 19:52.759
YOU'RE THE ONE LIVING
IN HER HOUSE, ASSHOLE.

19:52.759 --> 19:54.727
YOU DON'T KNOW SHIT
ABOUT WHAT'S GOING ON,

19:54.727 --> 19:56.596
SO I SUGGEST
YOU KEEP YOUR MOUTH SHUT.

19:56.596 --> 19:58.365
I KNOW YOU SLEEP HERE NOW,
DON'T YOU?

19:58.365 --> 19:59.899
DOESN'T TAKE A GENIUS
TO FIGURE OUT WHAT THAT MEANS.

19:59.899 --> 20:01.501
NATE WAS MY PARTNER.

20:01.501 --> 20:03.470
I'M LOOKING AFTER HIS FAMILY
THE WAY HE WOULD'VE WANTED.

20:03.470 --> 20:04.671
YEAH?
YOU GOT THAT?

20:04.671 --> 20:06.038
YEAH.
IS THAT CLEAR TO YOU?

20:06.038 --> 20:07.840
YEAH.
GET THE [BLEEP]
OUT OF HERE.

20:07.840 --> 20:10.209
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU NEED TO GET SOME HELP.

20:10.209 --> 20:12.745
DO I?
YEAH.

20:15.181 --> 20:16.616
SEE YA.

20:16.616 --> 20:17.984
YEAH.

20:22.255 --> 20:24.291
[ SIGHS ]

20:26.158 --> 20:29.228
SHIT.

20:29.228 --> 20:30.897
IT'S CALLED TREPHINATION,
OR BURR HOLES,

20:30.897 --> 20:32.332
TO RELIEVE THE PRESSURE.

20:32.332 --> 20:33.800
Henry: OKAY, BUT IF YOU'RE
GONNA DRILL IN MY HEAD,

20:33.800 --> 20:35.335
WHY NOT
JUST DIG THE BULLET OUT?

20:35.335 --> 20:36.936
YOU'RE STILL BLEEDING,
MR. WATTS.

20:36.936 --> 20:38.838
THIS HAS TO HAPPEN NOW.
THEN WE CAN PURSUE OUR OPTIONS.

20:38.838 --> 20:41.107
LIKE WHAT?
DR. BERNHEIMER
WILL BE TALKING TO YOU.

20:41.107 --> 20:42.309
NO.
WHY CAN'T YOU TELL ME?

20:42.309 --> 20:43.610
AND WHAT ABOUT THE GUY
AT CEDARS?

20:43.610 --> 20:45.144
WE'RE ALL STILL
REVIEWING THINGS.

20:45.144 --> 20:47.246
PLEASE LIE BACK.

20:48.348 --> 20:52.051
ALL ASLEEP.
PRETTY AMAZING, ACTUALLY.

20:52.051 --> 20:54.153
YOU'RE GOOD WITH KIDS,
SAMMY.

20:54.153 --> 20:55.588
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT THAT.

20:55.588 --> 20:58.691
I THINK THEY JUST SENSE
THAT I'M ONE OF THEM.

20:58.691 --> 21:02.261
YOU WENT AT STILES PRETTY GOOD
BACK THERE.

21:02.261 --> 21:03.463
OH.

21:03.463 --> 21:07.033
I THOUGHT
YOU WERE GONNA DECK HIM.

21:07.033 --> 21:09.836
THAT -- I'M SORRY.

21:09.836 --> 21:11.371
I'M AN IDIOT.

21:11.371 --> 21:13.673
NO. I'M SURE
YOU'RE JUST STRESSED

21:13.673 --> 21:15.475
ABOUT THE LINEUP TOMORROW.

21:15.475 --> 21:18.811
EVERYONE'S TALKING ABOUT IT,
HOW IT'S ALL UP TO YOU.

21:18.811 --> 21:20.613
WELL,
IF I RECOGNIZE HIM --

21:20.613 --> 21:23.516
I MEAN, IF IT'S THE GUY,
I'LL RECOGNIZE HIM.

21:23.516 --> 21:28.821
AND...IF I DO,
WE'LL TAKE HIM DOWN.

21:28.821 --> 21:31.458
I PROMISE.

21:37.229 --> 21:40.867
WHAT ARE WE DOING,
SAMMY?

21:45.304 --> 21:47.106
HEY, BUDDY.

21:47.106 --> 21:48.775
I'M THIRSTY.

21:48.775 --> 21:51.344
OKAY, BABY,
I'LL GET YOU WATER.

21:51.344 --> 21:55.047
SO, YOU'RE GONNA
BE MY DAD NOW?

21:55.047 --> 21:57.450
OKAY.
COME ON.

21:57.450 --> 21:59.819
LET'S GO INSIDE.

22:11.598 --> 22:14.867
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

22:59.712 --> 23:01.548
HEY.

23:01.548 --> 23:03.315
IF YOU WANT ME TO COME BACK,
I CAN.

23:03.315 --> 23:04.684
COME IN.
COME IN.

23:09.556 --> 23:12.925
THEY, UM --
THEY TELL YOU ABOUT...

23:15.361 --> 23:18.465
I GOT...

23:18.465 --> 23:22.301
TWO NEW HOLES...

23:22.301 --> 23:25.438
IN MY HEAD.

23:25.438 --> 23:27.940
EASE THE PRESSURE,
I GUESS.

23:27.940 --> 23:30.677
BEYOND THAT,
I DON'T KNOW.

23:30.677 --> 23:34.380
SEEMS LIKE NO ONE
WANTS TO OPERATE.

23:34.380 --> 23:38.284
OR NO ONE KNOWS HOW.

23:38.284 --> 23:39.786
YOU HEARD
ABOUT JESSICA?

23:39.786 --> 23:43.923
UH, NO, JUST, UM,
SHE'S ON HER WAY.

23:43.923 --> 23:46.025
YEAH, I KNOW.

23:46.025 --> 23:50.196
YOU KNOW WHAT SHE DOES
FOR A LIVING?

23:52.431 --> 23:55.134
WRITES CHILDREN'S BOOKS.

23:55.134 --> 24:00.272
REALLY GOOD ONES
ABOUT A LIZARD NAMED FIG.

24:00.272 --> 24:02.675
YOU HAVE ANY KIDS?
NO.

24:02.675 --> 24:05.778
THEN YOU PROBABLY NEVER HEARD
OF A LIZARD NAMED FIG.

24:05.778 --> 24:08.280
IT'S REALLY GOOD.

24:08.280 --> 24:10.617
IT'S HOW WE MET.

24:10.617 --> 24:15.287
I DID THE ILLUSTRATIONS
FOR HER SECOND BOOK.

24:15.287 --> 24:19.158
AND WE JUST...

24:19.158 --> 24:22.161
FELL IN LOVE.

24:22.161 --> 24:25.932
JUST JUMPED RIGHT INTO IT.

24:29.636 --> 24:33.239
STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
HOW LUCKY I GOT.

24:43.382 --> 24:46.619
WHAT WOULD YOU DO...

24:46.619 --> 24:49.522
IF YOU WERE ME?

24:49.522 --> 24:52.892
WOULD YOU
GO UNDER THE KNIFE

24:52.892 --> 24:57.830
FOR THE 1% CHANCE
AT LIVING,

24:57.830 --> 25:00.833
OR WOULD YOU TRY
TO HOLD OUT

25:00.833 --> 25:03.936
FOR A CHANCE
TO SAY GOODBYE?

25:05.572 --> 25:07.974
OH, I DON'T --

25:07.974 --> 25:09.809
I --

25:14.413 --> 25:16.849
I WAS IN LOVE ONCE.

25:16.849 --> 25:18.117
YEAH?

25:18.117 --> 25:21.754
YEAH, IT WAS
MY SECOND TRAINING OFFICER

25:21.754 --> 25:25.324
WHEN I JUST JOINED
THE FORCE, AND...

25:25.324 --> 25:27.727
HE WAS MARRIED WITH KIDS,

25:27.727 --> 25:31.764
AND WHEN HE DECIDED
TO LEAVE HIS WIFE...

25:31.764 --> 25:34.333
THINGS GOT UGLY
REAL FAST.

25:34.333 --> 25:36.836
WHAT HAPPENED?

25:36.836 --> 25:39.739
WE FIGURED IT OUT.

25:39.739 --> 25:43.743
WE FIGURED OUT A WAY
TO BE TOGETHER.

25:46.078 --> 25:48.948
AND THEN HE WAS KILLED
ON THE JOB.

25:48.948 --> 25:53.319
A SHOOTOUT
AT AN AUTO-PARTS STORE.

25:53.319 --> 25:56.222
IT WAS SENSELESS, BUT...

25:58.324 --> 26:00.627
BUT I HAD BEEN REASSIGNED.

26:00.627 --> 26:04.230
SO I WASN'T THERE
TO SAY GOODBYE.

26:05.765 --> 26:08.034
AND THAT...

26:12.471 --> 26:16.175
IF YOU LOVE HER...

26:16.175 --> 26:18.845
HOLD OUT.

26:18.845 --> 26:22.615
THAT'D BE MY ANSWER.

26:22.615 --> 26:25.117
I'M GONNA LET YOU
GET SOME REST, OKAY?

26:25.117 --> 26:27.319
DON'T -- DON'T.

26:27.319 --> 26:29.088
PLEASE.

26:44.136 --> 26:47.173
Jacoby: THIS WAS SET FOR 9:00.
IT'S NOW GOING ON 11:00.

26:47.173 --> 26:48.841
I DON'T WORK HERE, SIR.
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO

26:48.841 --> 26:50.342
TAKE THAT UP WITH
THE SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT.

26:50.342 --> 26:52.211
AND DON'T THINK I DON'T KNOW
THE IRREGULARITIES

26:52.211 --> 26:53.813
WITH MY CLIENT'S
TRAFFIC WARRANT

26:53.813 --> 26:55.414
WERE A DIRECT RESULT
OF YOUR STALLING.

26:55.414 --> 26:58.117
I'M JUST A COP, COUNSELOR.
FEWER WORDS WOULD BE GOOD.

26:58.117 --> 27:01.087
NOW, IF YOU COULD JUST STAND
THE [BLEEP] OVER THERE, PLEASE?

27:01.087 --> 27:02.321
THANK YOU.

27:04.223 --> 27:06.726
SO, WE GOOD TO GO?

27:06.726 --> 27:09.028
Sal: SAMMY?

27:12.098 --> 27:13.966
YEAH.

27:13.966 --> 27:15.334
YEAH.

27:15.334 --> 27:17.169
DETECTIVE BRYANT,

27:17.169 --> 27:21.874
DO YOU RECOGNIZE ANY OF THE
INDIVIDUALS STANDING BEFORE YOU?

27:24.410 --> 27:27.914
RIGHT BEFORE HE HIT NATE,

27:27.914 --> 27:30.549
HE SAID,
"TOMA [BLEEP] PUTO."

27:30.549 --> 27:35.021
COULD I HAVE NUMBER 2, 3
REPEAT THAT FOR ME?

27:36.455 --> 27:41.327
NUMBER 2, TAKE ONE STEP FORWARD
AND SAY, "TOMA [BLEEP] PUTO."

27:41.327 --> 27:43.195
TOMA [BLEEP] PUTO.

27:43.195 --> 27:47.533
STEP BACK.
OKAY, NOW NUMBER 3.

27:47.533 --> 27:49.869
TOMA [BLEEP] PUTO.

27:51.337 --> 27:57.076
S-- CAN 6 TAKE HIS HAND
OUT OF HIS POCKET?

27:57.076 --> 28:00.379
NUMBER 6, TAKE YOUR HAND
OUT OF YOUR POCKET.

28:05.484 --> 28:07.720
3.

28:09.221 --> 28:10.656
NUMBER 3.

28:10.656 --> 28:12.892
YOU'RE SAYING YOU RECOGNIZE
NUMBER 3?

28:12.892 --> 28:14.493
IT'S NUMBER 3.

28:14.493 --> 28:15.694
OKAY, WE'RE DONE.

28:15.694 --> 28:16.896
NUMBER 2.

28:16.896 --> 28:19.598
NUMBER 2.
I MEANT NUMBER 2.

28:19.598 --> 28:23.202
IT'S NUMBER 2.
OKAY?

28:23.202 --> 28:24.670
LET'S GO.

28:24.670 --> 28:27.139
NUMBER 2 IS AN INMATE HERE,
SAMMY.

28:27.139 --> 28:30.442
HE GOT EXTRA FOOD
FOR STANDING IN THE LINEUP.

28:42.154 --> 28:44.223
John: THAT'S --
THAT'S JUST GREAT. TERRIFIC.

28:44.223 --> 28:46.592
THANK YOU.
NO. YEAH.

28:46.592 --> 28:47.960
OKAY, YOU TOO.

28:47.960 --> 28:49.328
WELL, GOOD NEWS.

28:49.328 --> 28:53.065
SOME DESK JOCKEY
JUST FORGOT TO SIGN A FORM.

28:53.065 --> 28:56.635
SO THEY MOVED THE CRACK TRAILER
THIS MORNING.

28:56.635 --> 29:00.239
Ben: ALL RIGHT.

29:02.408 --> 29:04.844
SO NOW WE'RE GOING
TO DOUBLE-CHECK.

29:04.844 --> 29:08.347
YOU TRUST ANYTHING
THE CITY TELLS YOU?

29:08.347 --> 29:11.784
NO.

29:11.784 --> 29:13.685
Chickie:
GEEZ, THAT SUCKS.

29:13.685 --> 29:15.287
OKAY, BYE.

29:15.287 --> 29:18.357
NATE MORETTA --
THAT COP WHO GOT MURDERED?
YEAH.

29:18.357 --> 29:21.160
HIS PARTNER PICKED THE WRONG GUY
IN A LINEUP.

29:21.160 --> 29:23.262
OUCH!
NOTIFY THE SUICIDE HOTLINE.

29:23.262 --> 29:25.164
DEWEY.
I'M JUST SAYING, MAN.
YOU KNOW HOW IT IS.

29:25.164 --> 29:26.799
THEY'RE GONNA
BE WATCHING HIS ASS.

29:26.799 --> 29:31.337
DISPATCHER: All units and A35,
211 in progress, 1620 Fuega.

29:31.337 --> 29:32.604
LIGHT THEM UP.

29:32.604 --> 29:34.206
[ SIREN WAILING ]

29:35.707 --> 29:37.109
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

29:40.847 --> 29:42.381
FREEZE!
DROP THE KNIFE!

29:42.381 --> 29:44.016
DROP IT!

29:44.016 --> 29:46.552
FOLLOW ME IN THE CAR!

29:46.552 --> 29:49.889
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

29:49.889 --> 29:52.491
[ SIREN WAILING ]

29:52.491 --> 29:54.726
STOP!

29:54.726 --> 29:57.396
STOP RIGHT NOW!

30:01.600 --> 30:04.370
THAT'S IT.

30:14.080 --> 30:17.583
THANK YOU. [ SPEAKS SPANISH ]
I'M GONNA BORROW THIS.

30:17.583 --> 30:19.952
HEY, JAG-OFF.

30:31.197 --> 30:33.599
NOT RAMPART?
YOU'RE LEARNING.

30:33.599 --> 30:35.301
GIVE ME A HAND.

30:35.301 --> 30:36.735
MUCHACHOS...

30:36.735 --> 30:39.005
VENGA AYUDARNOS,
POR FAVOR.

30:40.106 --> 30:41.607
Chickie: STOP!

30:41.607 --> 30:43.876
[ SIREN WAILING ]

30:45.377 --> 30:47.613
[ TIRES SCREECH ]
HE'S GETTING IN A CAR.

30:47.613 --> 30:48.814
RIGHT BEHIND YOU, PARTNER.

30:48.814 --> 30:50.049
GOLD FORD.

30:50.049 --> 30:52.418
LICENSE PLATE -- VICTOR-4-7.

30:55.221 --> 30:56.488
GO!

31:06.532 --> 31:07.799
GRACIAS, AMIGO.

31:07.799 --> 31:09.635
GRACIAS.
YEAH.

31:13.872 --> 31:15.908
YEAH, THIS IS JOHN COOPER

31:15.908 --> 31:17.776
WITH THE LOS ANGELES
POLICE DEPARTMENT.

31:17.776 --> 31:19.178
YEAH, HOW YOU DOING?

31:19.178 --> 31:22.548
I GOT AN ABANDONED VEHICLE
BLOCKING THE ALLEY

31:22.548 --> 31:24.583
BEHIND 226 VERNON.

31:24.583 --> 31:26.318
YEAH.

31:26.318 --> 31:28.420
ALL RIGHT,
I APPRECIATE IT.

31:28.420 --> 31:31.991
CHICKIE: A35, we're in pursuit
of a gold Ford Contour,

31:31.991 --> 31:34.393
now westbound on Florence
at Brighton.

31:34.393 --> 31:37.196
A43,
SHOW US EN ROUTE TO BACK.

31:37.196 --> 31:39.165
MAN:
Suspect just turned,

31:39.165 --> 31:41.500
westbound on Selma
from Cahuenga.

31:41.500 --> 31:45.137
MAN #2: Air-3, what's the speed
of the suspect's vehicle,

31:45.137 --> 31:46.605
and what are the conditions?

31:46.605 --> 31:49.475
NO, NO, NO, DO NOT CALL OFF
THIS [BLEEP] CHASE!

31:49.475 --> 31:50.676
CLEAR!

31:50.676 --> 31:54.613
70, 75. Traffic's moderate,
non-residential.

31:54.613 --> 31:57.950
A43, SHOW US
AS A SECONDARY UNIT IN PURSUIT.

31:57.950 --> 32:00.286
Approaching a no-fly zone.
Got to back off.

32:00.286 --> 32:02.854
Primary unit,
you have it.
WE GOT THIS [BLEEP]

32:02.854 --> 32:04.256
[ TIRES SCREECH ]
CLEAR. WE'RE CLEAR.

32:04.256 --> 32:08.127
A35, SUSPECT HEADING
NORTHBOUND NOW -- SCHRADER.

32:08.127 --> 32:11.163
WE GOT THIS SON OF A BITCH.

32:11.163 --> 32:12.431
[ WAILING CONTINUES ]

32:12.431 --> 32:13.565
CLEAR!

32:13.565 --> 32:16.002
DEWEY!

32:16.002 --> 32:17.536
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

32:17.536 --> 32:18.704
DAMN!

32:18.704 --> 32:20.306
GOD DAMN.

32:21.507 --> 32:24.576
DAMN IT.
WE GOT TO KEEP GOING.
JESUS.

32:24.576 --> 32:26.245
WOMAN DOWN.

32:26.245 --> 32:28.847
SHE JUST CAME OUT OF NOWHERE!
SHIT!

32:28.847 --> 32:30.882
[ HORN HONKS ]

32:30.882 --> 32:33.152
[ SIREN WAILING ]

32:34.886 --> 32:37.189
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

32:38.324 --> 32:40.226
HEY!
FREEZE!

32:40.226 --> 32:42.194
LET ME SEE YOUR HANDS NOW!
GET YOUR HANDS UP!

32:42.194 --> 32:44.430
GET YOUR HANDS OUT OF THE CAR!
PUT YOUR HANDS UP!

32:44.430 --> 32:45.897
LET'S GO!
HANDS UP NOW!

32:45.897 --> 32:49.835
A43, SHOW US CODE 6,
CORNER OF YUCCA AND ARGYLE.

32:49.835 --> 32:52.004
DOES SHE HAVE A PULSE?

32:52.004 --> 32:53.739
OH, GOD.

32:53.739 --> 32:54.940
OH, GOD!

32:54.940 --> 32:56.142
[BLEEP]

32:56.142 --> 32:57.509
GOD DAMN IT!

32:59.445 --> 33:01.080
ONE, TWO...

33:01.080 --> 33:03.249
John: YOU GOT HIM?
YEAH, I GOT HIM,
I GOT HIM, I GOT HIM.

33:03.249 --> 33:05.017
ALL RIGHT,
WE GOT TWO PINNED.

33:05.017 --> 33:07.153
YOU OKAY, MA'AM?
SOMEBODY'S COMING, MA'AM.

33:07.153 --> 33:08.620
Woman:
NO, I CAN'T MOVE MY LEGS!

33:08.620 --> 33:10.489
OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

33:10.489 --> 33:12.058
19, 20...

33:12.058 --> 33:15.994
21, 22, 23, 24.

33:15.994 --> 33:17.896
COME ON, COME ON.
IT'S OVER.

33:17.896 --> 33:21.567
IT'S OVER, MAN.
IT'S OVER.

33:21.567 --> 33:23.235
SHE'S DEAD.

33:23.235 --> 33:25.271
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

33:53.332 --> 33:56.001
[ GROANS ]
EGGS.

33:56.001 --> 33:57.769
CAN I GET YOU SOMETHING?

33:57.769 --> 34:00.139
I FORGOT THEM
AT THE STORE.

34:00.139 --> 34:01.907
HOW COULD YOU
FORGET THAT?

34:01.907 --> 34:03.709
WEREN'T THEY
ON YOUR LIST?

34:03.709 --> 34:04.943
YEAH.

34:04.943 --> 34:06.712
YEAH, BUT...

34:06.712 --> 34:09.047
Jessica: HENRY.

34:09.047 --> 34:11.317
JESSICA.
GOD, BABY.

34:11.317 --> 34:12.918
HOW DO YOU FEEL?

34:12.918 --> 34:14.386
JESS.

34:14.386 --> 34:16.822
WHEN ARE YOU HAVING SURGERY?
WHAT'S -- UH...

34:16.822 --> 34:21.493
OH, I TOLD THEM I WAS GONNA WAIT
FOR YOU TO GET HERE.

34:21.493 --> 34:24.062
SO...

34:25.397 --> 34:28.467
DEWEY TOLD ME ALREADY, JOHN.
ALL PART OF GOD'S PLAN.

34:28.467 --> 34:30.902
DON'T MAKE ME TELL YOU
TO [BLEEP] OFF, TOO.

34:30.902 --> 34:32.804
LOOK, WHAT HAPPENED WAS TRAGIC,
ALL RIGHT?

34:32.804 --> 34:34.740
BUT WE DID
WHAT WE WERE SUPPOSED TO.

34:34.740 --> 34:36.342
WE LOST AIR SUPPORT.

34:36.342 --> 34:37.909
WE WERE PRIMARY.

34:37.909 --> 34:40.011
IT WAS MY RESPONSIBILITY.

34:40.011 --> 34:41.347
I COULD HAVE
CALLED IT OFF.

34:41.347 --> 34:43.115
SHE STEPPED
RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU.

34:43.115 --> 34:44.683
THERE WERE SIRENS,
LIGHTS FLASHING.

34:44.683 --> 34:47.153
YOU KNOW
THE FUNNIEST PART?

34:47.153 --> 34:50.122
I WASN'T GONNA BE A COP.

34:50.122 --> 34:53.292
I WAS JUST GONNA SURF.

34:53.292 --> 34:56.795
I DON'T KNOW.
BARTEND.

34:56.795 --> 35:02.301
BUT THEN GETTING PREGNANT,
MY MARRIAGE BLOWING UP.

35:02.301 --> 35:04.503
I HAD A KID.

35:07.273 --> 35:09.475
I NEEDED A JOB.

35:09.475 --> 35:13.145
THAT WAS ALL THIS WAS
SUPPOSED TO BE.

35:14.380 --> 35:18.083
HOW MANY SURFERS
RUN TOWARD GUNFIRE?

35:18.083 --> 35:20.552
HMM? HOW MANY?

35:22.154 --> 35:24.956
TEACHERS, BARTENDERS --

35:24.956 --> 35:27.226
THEY JUST JUMP IN THEIR CAR
AND GO AFTER THESE ASSHOLES?

35:27.226 --> 35:29.395
NO.

35:29.395 --> 35:34.533
NO, AND UNTIL THEY DO,
YOU CUT YOURSELF A BREAK.

35:36.635 --> 35:39.070
I-I GOT TO GO
PICK UP TRISTAN.

35:39.070 --> 35:41.773
IF NOT YOU, WHO?

35:41.773 --> 35:43.875
WHO, CHICKIE?

35:43.875 --> 35:48.414
WHO DESERVES
TO BE WEARING THAT UNIFORM?

35:48.414 --> 35:50.716
Nurse: UM, DETECTIVE?

35:50.716 --> 35:53.352
SHE WAS RIGHT THERE WITH HIM
WHEN HE DIED.

35:53.352 --> 35:54.853
I KNEW
YOU'D WANT TO KNOW.

35:54.853 --> 35:56.154
THANKS.

35:56.154 --> 35:57.656
AND, DETECTIVE...

35:57.656 --> 36:00.058
I COULDN'T HELP HEARING
WHAT YOU SAID TO HIM.

36:00.058 --> 36:01.193
IT WAS...

36:01.193 --> 36:02.694
IT WAS BEAUTIFUL.

36:02.694 --> 36:05.464
I'M JUST SORRY THAT YOU HAD TO
GO THROUGH THAT.

36:05.464 --> 36:07.733
I JUST MADE THAT UP,
ACTUALLY.

36:07.733 --> 36:11.036
JUST WANTED TO GIVE HIM
STRENGTH, YOU KNOW?

36:11.036 --> 36:12.271
REALLY?

36:12.271 --> 36:15.541
IT FELT SO HONEST
AND HEARTFELT AND...

36:15.541 --> 36:19.678
COPS --
GOOD STORYTELLERS.

36:25.817 --> 36:27.586
[ SIGHS ]

36:34.993 --> 36:38.096
WE AGREED THAT YOU
WOULD NOT COME HERE.

36:38.096 --> 36:39.731
I GOT NO PLACE TO GO.

36:39.731 --> 36:42.033
[ SCOFFS ]

36:42.033 --> 36:45.737
WELL, YOU CAN'T STAY HERE.
JESUS!

36:48.940 --> 36:51.009
WH--

36:51.009 --> 36:54.313
WHAT IS IT?

36:54.313 --> 36:57.983
I [BLEEP] UP.

36:57.983 --> 37:01.253
EVERYTHING I TOUCH...

37:01.253 --> 37:05.924
EVERYTHING
JUST TURNS TO SHIT.

37:05.924 --> 37:07.626
EVERYTHING.

37:07.626 --> 37:10.596
W--

37:10.596 --> 37:14.165
WHAT -- WHAT DID YOU DO?

37:14.165 --> 37:17.603
IT'S WHAT I DIDN'T --

37:17.603 --> 37:20.572
IT'S WHAT I COULDN'T --

37:21.873 --> 37:23.442
IT'S WHAT I COULDN'T DO.

37:23.442 --> 37:24.910
HEY, HEY.

37:24.910 --> 37:26.111
I COULDN'T.

37:26.111 --> 37:29.214
HEY. HEY. HEY.

37:29.214 --> 37:32.217
SAMMY. SAMMY.

37:32.217 --> 37:35.120
[ SOBBING ]

37:35.120 --> 37:37.323
COME ON.

37:38.924 --> 37:41.860
SAMMY.

37:54.473 --> 37:57.275
[ BRAKES SQUEAL ]

37:59.478 --> 38:01.279
HEY.
HEY.

38:01.279 --> 38:03.148
HOW YOU DOING?

38:03.148 --> 38:05.684
YOU CAME TO CHECK ON ME.

38:05.684 --> 38:08.320
COME ON.
I NEED A DRINK.

38:17.128 --> 38:20.332
YOU ALL RIGHT?

38:20.332 --> 38:23.802
HAVE YOU, UM...

38:23.802 --> 38:25.236
HEARD THE NEWS AT ALL
LATELY?

38:25.236 --> 38:28.106
DO YOU THAT THEY KICKED
THAT GUY IN THE MORETTA CASE?

38:28.106 --> 38:29.741
[ SCOFFS ]
YEAH, MAN.

38:29.741 --> 38:32.077
I GUESS WHEN IT RAINS,
IT POURS.

38:32.077 --> 38:37.115
YOU HEARD A PATROL COP KILLED
A PEDESTRIAN IN THE 77th?

38:37.115 --> 38:41.653
HIGH-SPEED CHASE.
SHE JUST WALKED INTO TRAFFIC.

38:41.653 --> 38:43.389
YEAH, I HEARD THAT.

38:43.389 --> 38:46.291
AND NOW I'M ABOUT
TO LOSE MY JOB

38:46.291 --> 38:49.528
FOR LEAKING PHOTOS
OF A DEAD CELEBRITY.

38:49.528 --> 38:52.230
ALL THESE YEARS
OF BEING A GOOD COP,

38:52.230 --> 38:54.165
AND THAT'S
MY GOOGLE HIT.

38:54.165 --> 38:55.501
LYDIA.

38:55.501 --> 38:59.738
NO, IT'S GONNA HAPPEN, RUSS.
I CAN FEEL IT.

38:59.738 --> 39:03.241
JUST ALL THE RAGE I FEEL,
YOU KNOW?

39:03.241 --> 39:05.276
JUST I'M UP ALL NIGHT.

39:05.276 --> 39:07.312
WHO COULD DO THIS?

39:07.312 --> 39:09.948
NOT JUST TO ME,
BUT TO US.

39:13.318 --> 39:14.853
I DID.

39:14.853 --> 39:18.390
COME ON, RUSS.
IT'S NOT FUNNY.

39:19.458 --> 39:21.026
I, UH, GAVE THEM
A COUPLE PHOTOS,

39:21.026 --> 39:23.094
AND THEY PAID ME
HALF A MILLION BUCKS.

39:26.998 --> 39:30.035
WHAT, WAS I GONNA BE A SECRETARY
THE REST OF MY LIFE?

39:30.035 --> 39:35.807
SCRAPE BY ON DISABILITY,
IF THEY EVEN GAVE IT TO ME?

39:35.807 --> 39:38.844
[BLEEP] IT, LYD.
I SAW MY CHANCE, SO I TOOK IT.

39:40.145 --> 39:43.281
IF I HAD KNOWN THAT THE PHOTOS
WERE FROM YOUR PHONE,

39:43.281 --> 39:44.716
I WOULDN'T HAVE DONE IT.

39:46.885 --> 39:50.789
I JUST TOLD FERNANDEZ
AN HOUR AGO,

39:50.789 --> 39:53.124
GOT MY ASS REAMED
BY THE CHIEF.

39:53.124 --> 39:56.928
TOOK THEM ALL OF A MINUTE
TO FIRE ME.

39:56.928 --> 40:00.599
AT LEAST IT HURTS A LOT LESS
WITH CASH IN THE BANK.

40:02.768 --> 40:04.536
YOU DID IT
FOR THE MONEY?

40:04.536 --> 40:07.539
NO. NO. NO!
I WOULDN'T --

40:08.707 --> 40:10.476
IT LOOKED LIKE
THAT ASSHOLE ACTOR

40:10.476 --> 40:12.077
CHOPPED HIS GIRLFRIEND'S
HEAD OFF.

40:12.077 --> 40:14.212
I MEAN,
ESPECIALLY CELEBRITIES --

40:14.212 --> 40:17.683
THEY HAVE THOSE LAWYERS
AND THOSE FANCY HANDLERS, AND...

40:17.683 --> 40:19.451
YOU KNOW,
THE PUBLIC HAS TO KNOW

40:19.451 --> 40:21.587
WHEN VICIOUS SHIT LIKE THAT
GOES DOWN.

40:24.422 --> 40:26.692
HE WAS INNOCENT.

40:26.692 --> 40:28.927
HE SHOT HIMSELF.

40:30.128 --> 40:32.531
I KNOW.
I COULDN'T HAVE PREDICTED THAT.

40:32.531 --> 40:34.466
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:35.501 --> 40:37.903
BUT THE BOTTOM LINE IS...

40:37.903 --> 40:39.971
I'M SORRY.

40:42.040 --> 40:47.178
I KNOW YOU WENT THROUGH A LOT
FOR THAT AND IT MESSED YOU UP.

40:47.178 --> 40:49.481
AND I WISH --

40:52.017 --> 40:54.185
I SHOULD'VE
TOLD YOU SOONER.

40:54.185 --> 40:55.921
THAT WAS WRONG.

41:02.728 --> 41:04.763
I DON'T EVEN KNOW YOU.

41:04.763 --> 41:05.997
LYDIA.

41:05.997 --> 41:07.899
I DON'T EVEN KNOW YOU,
DUDE.

41:07.899 --> 41:11.670
LYDIA, PLEASE.

41:11.670 --> 41:14.472
COME ON.
LYDIA!

41:14.472 --> 41:15.040
[ DOOR SLAMS ]
